Installing and compiling BfdAda
===============================

To compile BfdAda you'll need:

 - an Ada compiler (GNAT or gcc 4.6).

 - the binutils 2.22 installed for developpment
   (you need the bfd.h include; see binutils-dev package on Debian or Ubuntu)


Run the GNU configure command and build the library:

  ./configure
  make
  make check


You can install the library by using:

  make install

